mpians who have inspired millions.\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2595, \"end\": 2603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7342896949696872e-13, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No wonder\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"Keleti's name\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"other Olympians\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nations gather around sports, especially the Olympics, as a space where this kind of togetherness and fair completions are the most important things,\\\" Szemerey notes.\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nations\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"especially the Olympics\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"a space\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2726}, {\"ngram\": \"this kind\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"togetherness\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"completions\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2779}, {\"ngram\": \"the most important things\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2809}, {\"ngram\": \"Szemerey\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Keleti watches the Games, she takes a moment to remind us of the Olympics' greater purpose: uniting people, especially during global turmoil.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Keleti\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics' greater purpose\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngr